divs: sighting detailsfirst event, was one, apricot in color, moving north slow, 30 mph, like a flame, 15 minutes latter philippine fighter jets going same direction. 3 months latter again over manila, next event; week latter the 3 vee shapped ones flew over slow, we were on the roof of a 10 story condo. only visable because of the city lights reflection. thats more than i have seen in my entire life. my friend is a pilot from alaska, all his adult life, and he never seen one till now. nothing chassed the vee ones. thx for all you have done. been listening since art started 20 yeas now.
